##Yarn用户
 * hadoop
 * hbase
 * spark

```shell
groupadd hadoop
useradd -g hadoop hadoop
useradd -g hadoop spark
useradd -g hadoop hbase
```
##修改目录权限
```shell
chown hadoop:hadoop /yarn
chown hadoop:hadoop /yarn/app -R
chown hadoop:hadoop /yarn/data -R

chown hbase:hadoop /yarn/app/hbase -R
chown spark:hadoop /yarn/app/spark -R

chown hbase:hadoop /yarn/data/hbase -R
chown spark:hadoop /yarn/data/spark -R

```
##设置linux打开最大文件数
```shell
cat /etc/security/limits.conf #增加以下内容到文件中
root ulimit -Sn 10000
root ulimit -Hn 10000

```

##关闭iptables

```shell
chkconfig iptables off
/etc/init.d/iptables stop
```

##关闭SELinux

```shell
# setenforce 0
vim /etc/selinux/config
修改SELINUX为disable
```

